{"tid":338720,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓劇] 犯罪心理 討論區 (1)","createTime":"2017-07-28T11:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T08:42:44.000Z","uid":49311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef520c3b2ce4f086b73cf2df50b8bf6213b6b0b","tid":338720,"uid":49311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x74fuyng\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx74fuyng&h=4dffb5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《犯罪心理》（韓語：크리미널 마인드，英語：Criminal Minds），為韓國tvN於2017年7月26日起播出的水木連續劇，由《IRIS》楊允浩、《The Good Wife》李政孝導演執導與洪勝賢作家共同打造。此劇講述行為分析師們剖析最棘手的案件，分析兇手的心理和作案特徵，並在他們再次施暴前預測出他們的下一步行動，協助當地警察捉拿兇手的故事。[1][2]此劇翻拍自美國電視劇《犯罪心理》。<br />\n<br />\n主演：李準基, 文彩元, 孫賢周"},{"pid":"ca4435479fba7d2ece7b858e069a493ea473ea6a","tid":338720,"uid":49311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"第一集作為開頭唔算太好 不過第二集黎料  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n孫賢周啲戲真係掂  仲有飾演朴宰民個演員啲戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97f2295c08c1a3910662c44dd20f89e79f116f7","tid":338720,"uid":49311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"不過李善彬係呢套個妝真係唔係幾掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438fcbd768b28d880f41aeb345e9b5a1f97ccd09","tid":338720,"uid":49311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a94c15892c1bba1d8c5895510b6ae7c083a2655","tid":338720,"uid":128863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一集作為開頭唔算太好 不過第二集黎料  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n孫賢周啲戲真係掂  